{{- define "wake_sprint_complete" -}}
All planned sprint tasks have reached terminal state. Complete the sprint:

1. Read blackboard to confirm all planned tasks are MERGED, ABANDONED, or SUPERSEDED
2. Update sprint metrics: execute liza_update_sprint_metrics with {"agent_id": "{{.AgentID}}"}
3. Create checkpoint for human review: execute liza_sprint_checkpoint with {"agent_id": "{{.AgentID}}"}
4. The checkpoint will pause all agents and generate a sprint summary

Do NOT create new tasks or start new work. The sprint is complete.
{{- end -}}
